Package com.asemantics.rdfcoder.parser

This package defines a set of parser interfaces and implementations.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClassPath
    This class represents the class path of a parse Asset (a group of related libraries) to be parsed in block.
    CodeParser
    Base class for any Code Parser implementation.
    DirectoryParser
    Defines a scanner to parse content of entire directories.
    FileParser
    Base class for a File Parser.
    ImportsContext
    This class represents the imports of a class and it is able to fully qualify an object.
    JStatistics
    Decorator class collecting some statistics related to the processing of the Java asset.
    ObjectsTable
    This class defines a table to resolve objects.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ParserException
    This exception encapsulates every error raised by a parser.

Package com.asemantics.rdfcoder.parser Description
